250
0:10:49.16,000 --> 0:10:52,000
Donc, vous devez comprendre ce passé.

251
0:10:52.16,000 --> 0:10:54,000
Pensez à Disney encore.

252
0:10:54.16,000 --> 0:10:56,000
Disney,

